15) Definition of Done (Acceptance Criteria)
Rules
Runs on staging via deploy from develop.
Tested (unit/integration where relevant).
Observability confirmed (logs + Sentry).
Security checks: no secrets leaked; endpoints protected.
Meets UX requirements on mobile + desktop.
Docs updated (README + OpenAPI if API change).
MVP Acceptance Checklist
Catalog import works and produces a clear report.
PLP/PDP/search/filtering work reliably and fast.
Checkout + payment reliably creates orders.
Invoice PDF generated and downloadable.
Customer emails sent correctly.
Admin can manage orders and import status without developer help.

