Final Notes (Rules of Engagement)
	•	No patches on PROD. All changes go via PR → staging → production.
	•	Keep integration logic in backend services, never in the frontend.
	•	Everything must be documented: installation, env vars, API, deployment.
	•	Modular design is mandatory: suppliers will increase after INFORTISA.

